Class Queue<T>

java.lang.Object
Queue<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Generic type of data to store in Queue.
All Implemented Interfaces:
QueueInterface<T>
public class Queue<T> extends Object implements QueueInterface<T>
Generic Queue implemented using a linked list. Uses node to store elements in the queue.
